An 18-year-old man has been arrested for in connection with the murder of three members of the same family. CAPE TOWN - An 18-year-old man has been arrested in connection with the murder of three members of the same family in De Aar.The bodies of 40-year-old Glenwill Makaleni, his wife Gladys and their 10-year-old son Gladwill were discovered in their home in the early hours of Saturday morning.Northern Cape police spokesperson Mohale Ramatseba says the deceased s home was locked from the inside when police arrived on the scene. We can confirm that [a] person was arrested in connection with the murder of the three people in De Aar and will appear in the De Aar Magistrates Court soon. The investigation is at a sensitive stage and we can t divulge much. (Edited by Shimoney Regter)